ed="T" n="0741a25"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0741a25"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042147">京師大安國寺</placeName><persName key="A009664">端甫</persName>傳<ptr target="#n920"/></head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0741a26"/><persName key="A009664">釋端甫</persName>，俗姓趙氏，<placeName key="PL000000044976">天水</placeName>人也。世為<placeName key="PL000000044976">秦</placeName>著姓<lb
ed="T" n="0741a27"/>焉。初，母<persName key="A022136">張<roleName>夫人</roleName></persName>夢梵僧謂曰：「當生貴子。」即<lb
ed="T" n="0741a28"/>出囊中舍利使吞之。及誕，所夢僧白晝入<lb
ed="T" n="0741a29"/>其室，摩其頂曰：「必當大興法教。」言訖而滅。<pb ed="T" n="0741b" xml:id="T50.2061.0741b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0741b01"/>既成人，高顙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g903"/>深目，大頤方口，長六尺五寸，其<lb
ed="T" n="0741b02"/>音如鐘。夫將欲荷<persName key="A002799">如來</persName>之菩提<ptr type="glossary" target="#g195"/>，鑿生靈之<lb
ed="T" n="0741b03"/>耳目，固必有殊祥奇表歟？始<date key="j20055842005948" when-iso="0779">十歲</date>，依<placeName key="PL000000042324">崇福<lb
ed="T" n="0741b04"/>寺</placeName><persName key="A009668">道悟禪師</persName>為沙彌。<date key="j20081412008505" when-iso="0786">十七</date>正度為比丘，隷<lb
ed="T" n="0741b05"/><placeName key="PL000000042147">安國寺</placeName>。受具於<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName><persName key="A001417">照律師</persName>，學毘尼於<placeName key="PL000000042324">崇<lb
ed="T" n="0741b06"/>福寺</placeName><persName key="A001261">昇律師</persName>，傳《唯識》於<placeName key="PL000000042147">安國寺</placeName><persName key="A018088">素法師</persName>，通《涅<lb
ed="T" n="0741b07"/>槃經》於<placeName key="PL000000042295">福林寺</placeName><persName key="A009671">崟法師</persName>。<persName key="A009664">甫</persName>又夢梵僧以舍利<lb
ed="T" n="0741b08"/>滿瑠璃器，使吞之，且曰：「三藏大教，盡貯<ref type="person" target="#A009664">汝</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0741b09"/>腹矣。」自是經、律、論無敵於當時，囊括川注，<lb
ed="T" n="0741b10"/>逢源會委<ptr type="glossary" target="#g910"/>，滔滔然莫能濟其畔岸矣。夫將<lb
ed="T" n="0741b11"/>欲伐株<anchor xml:id="beg0741sgsz1"/>杌<anchor xml:id="end0741sgsz1"/>於情田<ptr type="glossary" target="#g826"/>，雨甘露於法種者，固必<lb
ed="T" n="0741b12"/>有勇智宏辯歟？無何<ptr type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，謁<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000005250">清涼</placeName>，眾聖<lb
ed="T" n="0741b13"/>皆現；演大經於<placeName key="PL000000003794">太原</placeName>，傾都畢會。<persName key="A004215">德宗皇帝</persName>聞<lb
ed="T" n="0741b14"/>其名，徵之，一見大悅，常出入禁中，與儒道<lb
ed="T" n="0741b15"/>議論，賜紫方袍。歲時錫施，異於他等。復詔<lb
ed="T" n="0741b16"/>侍<ref type="person" target="#A004380">皇太子</ref>於東朝。<persName key="A004380">順宗皇帝</persName>深仰其風，親之<lb
ed="T" n="0741b17"/>若昆弟，相與臥起，恩禮特隆。<persName key="A002120">憲宗皇帝</persName>數幸<lb
ed="T" n="0741b18"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000042147">其寺</ref>，待<ref type="person" target="#A009664">之</ref>若賓友。常承顧問，注納偏厚。而<lb
ed="T" n="0741b19"/><persName key="A009664">甫</persName>符彩超邁，辭理響捷，迎合上旨，皆契真<lb
ed="T" n="0741b20"/>乘，雖造次<ptr type="glossary" target="#g619"/>應對，未甞不以闡揚為務。繇<lb
ed="T" n="0741b21"/>是<ptr type="glossary" target="#g911"/><ref type="person" target="#A002120">天子</ref>益知<persName key="A002799">佛</persName>為大聖人，其教有大不思<lb
ed="T" n="0741b22"/>議事。當是時朝廷方削平<placeName key="PL000000000214">區夏</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g912"/>，縛<persName key="A010372">吳</persName>斡<placeName key="PL000000034805">蜀</placeName><ptr target="#n416"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0741b23"/>瀦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g232"/><placeName key="PL000000026334">蔡</placeName>蕩<placeName key="PL000000021665">鄆</placeName><ptr target="#n416"/>，而<ref type="person" target="#A002120">天子</ref>端拱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g913"/>無事。詔<persName key="A009664">甫</persName>率緇屬<lb
ed="T" n="0741b24"/>迎真骨於靈山<ptr target="#n914"/>，開法場於祕殿，為人請福，<lb
ed="T" n="0741b25"/>親奉香燈。既而刑不殘，兵不黷，赤子無愁<lb
ed="T" n="0741b26"/>聲，蒼海無驚<anchor xml:id="beg0741001"/>波<anchor xml:id="end0741001"/>，蓋參用真宗以毘大政<lb
ed="T" n="0741b27"/>之明効也。夫將欲顯大不思議之道，輔大<lb
ed="T" n="0741b28"/>有為之君，固必有冥符<ptr type="glossary" target="#g799"/>玄契歟？掌內殿法<lb
ed="T" n="0741b29"/>儀，錄左街僧事，以標表淨眾者凡一十年。<pb ed="T" n="0741c" xml:id="T50.2061.0741c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0741c01"/>講《涅槃》、《唯識》經論，處當仁<ptr type="glossary" target="#g915"/>傳授宗主，以開<lb
ed="T" n="0741c02"/>誘道俗者，凡一百六十座。運三密<ptr type="glossary" target="#g94"/>於瑜伽<ptr type="glossary" target="#g93"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0741c03"/>契無生於悉地<ptr target="#n148"/>，日持諸部十餘萬遍，指淨<lb
ed="T" n="0741c04"/>土為息肩<ptr type="glossary" target="#g916"/>之地，嚴金經為報法之恩。前<lb
ed="T" n="0741c05"/>後供施數十百萬，悉以崇飾殿宇，窮極雕<lb
ed="T" n="0741c06"/>繪。而方丈單床，靜慮自得。貴臣盛族皆所依<lb
ed="T" n="0741c07"/>慕，豪俠工賈莫不瞻嚮，薦金寶以致誠，<lb
ed="T" n="0741c08"/>仰端嚴而<anchor xml:id="beg0741sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0741sgsz2"/>足，日有千數，不可殫書。而<lb
ed="T" n="0741c09"/><persName key="A009664">甫</persName>即眾生以觀佛，離四相<ptr target="#n917"/>以修善，心下如<lb
ed="T" n="0741c10"/>地，坦無丘陵，王、公、輿、臺<ptr target="#n918"/>皆以誠接。議者以<lb
ed="T" n="0741c11"/>為成就常不輕<ptr type="glossary" target="#g919"/>行者，唯<persName key="A009664">甫</persName>而已矣。夫將欲<lb
ed="T" n="0741c12"/>駕橫海之大航，拯迷<anchor xml:id="beg0741002"/>途<anchor xml:id="end0741002"/>於彼岸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g437"/>者，固必<lb
ed="T" n="0741c13"/>有奇功妙道歟？以<date key="j20266052026605" when-iso="0836-07-21">開成元年六月一日</date>，西<lb
ed="T" n="0741c14"/>向右脇而滅，當暑而尊容若生，終夕而異<lb
ed="T" n="0741c15"/>香猶欝。<date key="j20266402026640" when-iso="0836-08-25">其年七月六日</date>，遷於<placeName key="PL000000055649">長樂</placeName>之南原。遺<lb
ed="T" n="0741c16"/>命荼毘，得舍利三百餘粒，方熾而神光月皎，<lb
ed="T" n="0741c17"/>既燼而靈骨珠圓。賜諡曰「<persName key="A009664">大達</persName>」，塔曰「<placeName key="PL000000055653">玄祕</placeName>」。<lb
ed="T" n="0741c18"/>俗壽六十七，僧臘可數。門弟子僧尼約千餘<lb
ed="T" n="0741c19"/>輩，或講論玄言，或紀綱大寺，修禪秉律，分<lb
ed="T" n="0741c20"/>作人師，五十其徒，皆為達者。<date from-iso="0841" key="j20282682030460" to-iso="0847">會昌</date>中相國<lb
ed="T" n="0741c21"/><persName key="A003624">裴<roleName>公</roleName>休</persName>為碑頌德焉。</p>
